text: Ærest upp of colenea æt þære lange hegge ænde.
Up to boiwic fram boiwic to þam cupe fram ðam cupe into þam middelan ðere strete.
Andlang strete into hilce sloð fram hilcen sloð to Tiðulfes treow fram Tiðulfes treow to hæselhyrste gate.
Fram þanon to þam fulen gate.
Ðanon into þam west heale swa to buleðe heige fram buleðe heige to lusebyrge swa ðanon into cealden lea.
And swa eft into colenea be midelen streame.
Ðæ offa mercene reccere gebocede sancte petre & þam hirede on westmunstre on ece erfe.
